          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is an average of the selling price ranges listed by 12 suppliers on www.alibaba.com (accessed on the 2017-09-19). The prices were listed in USD and were converted to EUR with the live mid-market exchange rate of 0.834 EUR/USD (obtained from www.xe.com on the 2017-09-19).</comment>
